 China strengthen ties |work=[[The New Times (Rwanda)|The New Times]] |location=Kigali |url=http://mail.newtimes.co.rw/news/index.php?i=15358&a=66925 |accessdate=29 May 2013 |ref=harv |url-status=dead |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140320190207/http://mail.newtimes.co.rw/news/index.php?i=15358&a=66925 |archivedate=20 March 2014 }}\n* {{cite book |last=Gourevitch |first=Philip |year=2000 |title=We Wish To Inform You That Tomorrow We Will Be Killed With Our Families |edition=Reprint |location=London; New York, N.Y. |publisher=Picador |isbn=978-0-330-37120-9 |url=https://books.google.com/?id=8OiMfpTiApQC |ref=harv}}\n* {{cite web |author=Global Witness |year=2013 |title=Putting principles into practice: Risks and opportunities for conflict-free sourcing in eastern Congo |authorlink=Global Witness |url=http://www.globalwitness.org/sites/default/files/library/Putting%20principles%20into%20practice.pdf |accessdate=16 May 2013 |ref=harv}}\n* {{cite news |last=Grant |first=Richard |date=22 July 2010 |title=Paul Kagame: Rwanda's redeemer or ruthless dictator? |location=London |work=[[The Daily Telegraph]] |url=https://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/worldnews/africaandindianocean/rwanda/7900680/Paul-Kagame-Rwandas-redeemer-or-ruthless-dictator.html |accessdate=28 February 2013 |ref=harv}}\n* {{cite news|author=Great Lakes Voice |date=12 January 2010 |title=Kagame says Gen Kayumba Nyamwasa, Col Karegyeya masterminds of Kigali grenade attack |url=http://greatlakesvoice.com/kagame-says-gen-kayumba-nyamwasacol-karegyeya-masterminds-of-kigali-grenade-attack/ |accessdate=9 February 2013 |ref=harv |url-status=dead |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140320192016/http://greatlakesvoice.com/kagame-says-gen-kayumba-nyamwasacol-karegyeya-masterminds-of-kigali-grenade-attack/ |archivedate=20 March 2014 }}\n* {{cite news |last=Henley |first=Jon |date=31 October 2007 |title=Scar tissue |work=The Guardian |url=https://www.theguardian.com/world/2007/oct/31/rwanda.theatre |accessda