k (II) |title=Rwanda |work=Data |authorlink=World Bank |url=http://data.worldbank.org/country/rwanda |accessdate=16 February 2012 |ref=harv}}\n* {{cite web|author=World Bank (III) |year=2012 |title=Economy Rankings |authorlink=World Bank |url=http://www.doingbusiness.org/rankings |accessdate=27 February 2013 |ref=harv |url-status=dead |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150206025936/http://www.doingbusiness.org/rankings |archivedate=6 February 2015 }}\n* {{cite web |author=World Bank (IV) |year=2012 |title=Ease of doing business index |authorlink=World Bank |url=http://data.worldbank.org/indicator/IC.BUS.EASE.XQ |accessdate=27 February 2013 |ref=harv}}\n* {{cite book |author=World Health Organization (WHO) (I) |year=2009 |title=WHO Country Cooperation Strategy, 2009\u20132013: Rwanda |isbn=978-92-9031-135-5 |authorlink=World Health Organization |url=http://www.who.int/countryfocus/cooperation_strategy/ccs_rwa_en.pdf | ref = {{sfnRef|WHO (I)|2009}} }}\n* {{cite journal |author=World Health Organization (WHO) (II) |year=2008 |title=Sharing the burden of sickness: mutual health insurance in Rwanda |journal=Bulletin of the World Health Organization |issn=0042-9686 |volume=86 |issue=11 |pages=817\u2013908 |url=http://www.who.int/bulletin/volumes/86/11/08-021108/en/index.html | ref = {{sfnRef|WHO (II)|2008}} }}\n* {{cite news |author=World Review |date=10 January 2013 |title=Paul Kagame guides Rwanda out of war and poverty |authorlink=World Review |url=http://www.worldreview.info/content/paul-kagame-guides-rwanda-out-war-and-poverty |accessdate=4 November 2010 |ref=harv |url-status=dead |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130428061823/http://www.worldreview.info/content/paul-kagame-guides-rwanda-out-war-and-poverty |archivedate=28 April 2013 |df=dmy-all }}\n{{refend}}\n\n==External links==\n{{Commons}}\n* {{Official website|www.paulkagame.com}}\n* {{C-SPAN|paulkagame}}\n* {{Charlie Rose view|6465}}\n* {{IMDb name|1879094}}\n* {{Worldcat id|lccn-nr97-6324}}\n* 